WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.910
The stakeholders for available, reliant,

00:00:02.910 --> 00:00:06.780
and resilient systems are almost every function in a company.

00:00:06.780 --> 00:00:10.530
Your customers be able to depend on your platform to be

00:00:10.530 --> 00:00:14.250
running and stable is going to be critical to your overall success.

00:00:14.250 --> 00:00:17.310
Most software platforms have service level agreements,

00:00:17.310 --> 00:00:21.060
or SLAs, that are critical to business stakeholders.

00:00:21.060 --> 00:00:23.850
All business functions tend to be concerned with

00:00:23.850 --> 00:00:27.090
a company's SLAs as they have widespread impact.

00:00:27.090 --> 00:00:31.050
The business both expects its vendors to meet their SLAs,

00:00:31.050 --> 00:00:35.565
and it is vital for a company to achieve its published SLAs,

00:00:35.565 --> 00:00:40.420
in order to meet contractual obligations and support customers.

